{"tid":611854,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解d懶高級嘅餐廳中意食客手動沖奶茶？","createTime":"2018-03-31T12:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T16:56:11.000Z","uid":162853,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fa75e9b7d42f8b4b444287314876160a83a0e674","tid":611854,"uid":162853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:36:17.000Z","msg":"去親呢d餐廳食嘢叫奶茶嘅話<br />\n佢地硬係中意將茶同奶分開上(多數都比鮮奶)<br />\n自已試過溝好多次<br />\n無論多奶、少奶、all in奶<br />\n都係溝唔出平時茶記嗰種奶茶嘅味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以佢地上奶茶嗰陣一見到係茶奶分開，仲要佢比d鮮奶稀到好似溝左水咁稀嗰陣<br />\n就好想一嘢倒曬d奶落口再噴落個伙計度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心你班柒頭咪咁懶 沖好先拎上嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20090521/large/21ec3p2n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20090521%2Flarge%2F21ec3p2n.jpg&h=ec6f351b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43a0b3a36e7ce8b9d45ae9a646c62cf36ffb6c8b","tid":611854,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"噉你又去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要屌又要食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4cae830fd442076757bf12b5c07eff96f1f1ef","tid":611854,"uid":5375,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:41:46.000Z","msg":"你係咪on9<br />\n餐廳飲既食英式奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b117ef89726eaf1e0dc5be95d33f59486f6803e","tid":611854,"uid":38550,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:44:57.000Z","msg":"佢幫你沖都一樣沖唔到茶記奶茶<br />\n茶底同奶根本唔同<br />\n<br />\n不如你又問下台式手搖沖唔沖到茶記奶茶出嚟"},{"pid":"cb79b2f42dfa55583630327ae8d5ba10ef1a0b53","tid":611854,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:46:23.000Z","msg":"m記都有分兩隻奶菜啦"},{"pid":"4d78709ab7f9203169e2298ed76c58a10972fbf2","tid":611854,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:47:44.000Z","msg":"想講其實係兩樣野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246f3f3210650d91a317ee5cc90d51d62c6ff797","tid":611854,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68a2f3f0093ead7879094c98fb1e4e7d6f08d093","tid":611854,"uid":71824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:51:01.000Z","msg":"自已溝果種好難飲  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3932d9ae0864dd3fcec858adbfbf8e3e20fe1097","tid":611854,"uid":45431,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:49:55.000Z","msg":"屌，人地serve西茶你就要人地做茶餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本係兩樣完全唔撚同既嘢<br />\n<br />\n食生炒糯米飯嗰時你唔屌人地唔連埋塊荷葉俾你?糯米雞有葉架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a45bf23d42171b3fa05099a71dbebac609f5750","tid":611854,"uid":51105,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T16:02:58.000Z","msg":"鬼佬奶茶同港式奶茶都未識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97fa21e755c2f5e7bdcc6bacbfcb029ec9bc40a","tid":611854,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T16:13:11.000Z","msg":"樓主今年幾歲？"},{"pid":"2509db70aaba65c50776b159ac0b310e047365b6","tid":611854,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T16:14:20.000Z","msg":"茶記嗰d茶膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185832170d